name: Yeniduzen print subscription login
description: So @yeniduzen is one of the older and popular newspapers in the country and I imagined that they had a landing page where people could subscribe to have print copies of their paper delivered to their addresses rather than the paper just printing plenty of copies and hoping to sell like they currently do (and so they can focus more resources on digital). Anyways if such a site existed, this is what I imagined it would look like.
